# Build artifacts and crash/timeout/OOM dumps from local `cargo fuzz run` /
# `cargo fuzz build` — never committed, regenerated on demand.
target
artifacts

# Deliberately NOT ignoring `corpus/`: `fuzz/corpus/fix_decode/` holds the
# COMMITTED adversarial regression corpus (#042) — a small, hand-curated set of
# fixtures, generated by `tests/fix_adversarial.rs` (`UPDATE_CORPUS=1 cargo test
# --test fix_adversarial`) and shared as the seed corpus for both the CI `fuzz`
# job and the adversarial-fixture typed-reject test. If a long local `cargo fuzz
# run` session against this directory produces many additional auto-minimized
# entries you do not intend to commit, `git status`/`git add` them selectively
# rather than blanket-ignoring the directory.
